{"tid":1295325,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"便衣警：警察執行職務唔需要展示委任證！！","createTime":"2019-07-08T03:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T04:41:48.000Z","uid":212626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4ef1d044d2e428ecd7e4addb99c8dc7b5c07f814","tid":1295325,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:46:08.000Z","msg":"網民昨日（7日）發起反修訂《逃犯條例》遊行，由尖沙咀太空館旁的梳士巴利花園遊行到西九龍高鐵站外。及至晚上，示威者轉往旺角佔據彌敦道等道路，警方武力清場，有現場人士頭破血流。有示威者質疑警員沒佩戴委任證，該警員稱：「警察執行職務時，係唔需要展示委任證。」<br />\n<br />\nTOPick正就事件向警方查詢，暫未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚上11時許，防暴警一度在創興廣場外的彌敦道與示威者對峙，一名警員身穿便服，戴有寫上「Police」字眼的頭盔及圓盾，身上無警員編號或委任證。他與多名軍裝警參與清場行動。<br />\n<br />\n示威者質疑該名便衣警身份，要求他出示委任證，該便衣警員稱：<span style=\"color: red;\">警察執行職務時，係唔需要展示委任證！</span><br />\n<br />\n有傳媒所見，在彌敦道北行線推進的防暴警察，當中16人至少有6人沒佩戴委任證。<br />\n<br />\n據《警察通例》第20章「警署與各科組日常處理的事務」列明，<span style=\"color: red;\">警務人員只要擬進行的工作不妨礙人員妥為保管委任證，警務人員在任何時候均須隨身攜帶委任證</span>。便衣人員不論是否當值，在與巿民接觸和行使警察權力時，<span style=\"color: red;\">必須表明身分及出示委任證</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uq6WbXZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuq6WbXZ.jpg&h=2eff4f9f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C5gCFRp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC5gCFRp.png&h=7f9d453e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2394577/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2394577%2F&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V74BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=d0131eca\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2394577/</a>"},{"pid":"b13cbacf44b8ce4d3ed0c11a3cb92539b68a2c50","tid":1295325,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:47:55.000Z","msg":"返去重讀中五啦垃圾狗"},{"pid":"bd7ce2b61d093dcf39d600c96a8ea5c36b10b7db","tid":1295325,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5ab31a5a78ba8f4a509cc9e19f47c22f9b9552","tid":1295325,"uid":254594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:49:46.000Z","msg":"咁可以合法幫佢解除武裝<br />\n我點知你係唔係示威者扮警察製造混亂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e887cb4ac5e7fd8dee2674424030515f931c5b3","tid":1295325,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:59:06.000Z","msg":"一睇就知唔係警察黎啦 如果佢真係警察呀 我願意所有建制議員立即白頭人送黑頭人呀！！！"},{"pid":"0ae5d578cb55f95479ef6cbbc7d0490c2a8b6fc3","tid":1295325,"uid":42252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:03:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港警察 人渣垃圾</span></span>"},{"pid":"d179b5b6d3e5845125fc0266682a78be8e529fd9","tid":1295325,"uid":234944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:05:12.000Z","msg":"偽進仔背唔到書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a549093b131946d91ccc34c744cfe968e8a5fa1","tid":1295325,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:39:52.000Z","msg":"Wave哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWave Cheung Wai Ho<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1295447/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1295447/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5ddfddd8eee60039ca77d2e710b6cbe91ffcccaf","tid":1295325,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:41:48.000Z","msg":"咁張委任證係咩時候用?<br />\n1 睇醫生<br />\n2 銀行借錢"}]}